    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Chakra Control (Body)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 19 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 7 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 19</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, E</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You push out a mass of wild Chakra, knocking back all creatures 1d4+1 x 5ft away from you and having them fall prone. This technique registers as a Strong Chakra activity for those sensing Chakra.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 4 Chakra once to deal 2d6 force damage to all creatures in the area (no save).</p>\n\n",
